---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us | SF Travels - Redefining Premium Mobility in Bangalore"
  description="Learn about the legacy of SF Travels. Built on absolute safety, transparent slab rate pricing, exceptional chauffeur hospitality, and executive corporate fleet transport."
>
  

  <main class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden pt-12 text-slate-800">
    <section class="relative min-h-[50vh] flex items-center justify-center pt-20 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0"
            style="background-image: url('https://horizons-cdn.hostinger.com/e3da7081-89fa-4296-8e0b-208ae94398b5/bda0fdb8b258bf205c0653b2583c1ec0.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat;">
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/65 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/80 via-black/50 to-black/70 z-10 pointer-events-none">
        </div>
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 relative z-20 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight drop-shadow-lg">About Us
            </h1>
            <p
                class="text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-white/90 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed drop-shadow-md">
                Your trusted partner for reliable and comfortable transportation in Bangalore</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-white overflow-hidden">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-16">
                <div class="lg:w-1/2"><span
                        class="text-[#1E2D5A] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm mb-2 block">Who We Are</span>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
                    <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 space-y-4">
                        <p>SF Travels has been serving Bangalore with premium taxi and vehicle rental
                            services. What started as a small venture has grown into one of the most trusted
                            transportation service providers in the city, thanks to our commitment to quality and
                            customer satisfaction.</p>
                        <p>We understand that transportation is more than just getting from point A to point B. It's
                            about comfort, safety, reliability, and peace of mind. That's why we've built our business
                            on these core principles, ensuring every journey with us is a pleasant experience.</p>
                        <p>Today, we serve thousands of satisfied customers ranging from individual travelers to
                            corporate clients, providing everything from airport transfers to outstation trips, local
                            rentals to event transportation.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="lg:w-1/2 w-full">
                    <div class="relative group">
                        <div
                            class="absolute -inset-4 bg-[#1E2D5A]/20 rounded-2xl transform rotate-3 -z-10 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-6">
                        </div><img
                            src="https://horizons-cdn.hostinger.com/e3da7081-89fa-4296-8e0b-208ae94398b5/17d45fe9289d06ad8c7db9829895c83d.png"
                            alt="SF Travels Premium Office"
                            class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-2xl object-cover transform transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-[1.01]">
                        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-xl hidden md:block">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                <div class="bg-green-100 p-2 rounded-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                        width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                                        stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                        class="w-6 h-6 text-[#1E2D5A]">
                                        <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"></circle>
                                        <path d="M15.477 12.89 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"></path>
                                    </svg></div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium">Experience</p>
                                    <p class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Premium Quality</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md border-t-4 border-[#1E2D5A]">
                    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">To provide safe, reliable, and comfortable transportation
                        services that exceed customer expectations. We strive to make every journey pleasant and
                        hassle-free by maintaining the highest standards of service quality and professionalism.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md border-t-4 border-slate-800">
                    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Vision</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">To be the most preferred transportation service provider in
                        Bangalore and beyond, known for our commitment to excellence, innovation, and customer
                        satisfaction. We aim to set new benchmarks in the travel and tourism industry.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-white">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 sm:mb-12 text-center">Our Core Values</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 sm:gap-10">
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                        <div class="bg-green-50 p-3 rounded-lg flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                                stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                class="w-8 h-8 text-[#1E2D5A]">
                                <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"></path>
                            </svg></div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Safety First</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">Well-maintained vehicles and
                                verified professional drivers ensure your safety.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                        <div class="bg-green-50 p-3 rounded-lg flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                                stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                class="w-8 h-8 text-[#1E2D5A]">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                                <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
                            </svg></div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Punctuality</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">We value your time and ensure
                                on-time service for all bookings.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                        <div class="bg-green-50 p-3 rounded-lg flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                                stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                class="w-8 h-8 text-[#1E2D5A]">
                                <path
                                    d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z">
                                </path>
                            </svg></div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Customer Care</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">Your satisfaction is our
                                priority with 24/7 customer support.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                        <div class="bg-green-50 p-3 rounded-lg flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                                stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                class="w-8 h-8 text-[#1E2D5A]">
                                <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"></circle>
                                <path d="M15.477 12.89 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"></path>
                            </svg></div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Quality Service</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">Premium vehicles and
                                professional service at competitive prices.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Why Choose Us</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div
                        class="flex items-start space-x-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-transparent hover:border-[#1E2D5A]/30 transition-colors">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="w-5 h-5 text-[#1E2D5A] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
                            <path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Wide Fleet Selection</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">From sedans to luxury buses, we have vehicles for every
                                need.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex items-start space-x-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-transparent hover:border-[#1E2D5A]/30 transition-colors">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="w-5 h-5 text-[#1E2D5A] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
                            <path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Professional Drivers</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Experienced, courteous, and well-trained chauffeurs.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex items-start space-x-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-transparent hover:border-[#1E2D5A]/30 transition-colors">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="w-5 h-5 text-[#1E2D5A] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
                            <path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">24/7 Availability</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Round-the-clock service for all your travel needs.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex items-start space-x-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-transparent hover:border-[#1E2D5A]/30 transition-colors">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="w-5 h-5 text-[#1E2D5A] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
                            <path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Transparent Pricing</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">No hidden charges, clear pricing for all services.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex items-start space-x-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-transparent hover:border-[#1E2D5A]/30 transition-colors">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="w-5 h-5 text-[#1E2D5A] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
                            <path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Well-Maintained Vehicles</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Regular maintenance and cleaning for your comfort.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex items-start space-x-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-transparent hover:border-[#1E2D5A]/30 transition-colors">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="w-5 h-5 text-[#1E2D5A] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
                            <path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Customer Support</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Dedicated team ready to assist you anytime.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
